[Study Group] Bayesian Statistics with the Rethinking Material 2
Why not run a model for each data category?
1. Decrease in accuracy of model parameters that are estimated independent of categories
2. Lacking the uncertainty associated with category-splits themselves
3. Model comparison only possible when model and variants thereof use same data
4. Reducing individual sample sizes hurt model accuracy overall
